Sub-NonRole
===========

Created:      2013-01-03
Home page:    <https://metacpan.org/release/Sub-NonRole>
Bug tracker:  <https://github.com/tobyink/p5-sub-nonrole/issues>
Maintainer:   Toby Inkster (TOBYINK) <tobyink@cpan.org>

0.006	2022-06-17

 [ Packaging ]
 - Remove dependency on Sub::Identity which has not been needed for a
   while.

0.005	2022-06-17

 - Updated: Use Role::Hooks instead of MooX::CaptainHook.

0.004	2014-09-10

 [ Packaging ]
 - Switch to Dist::Inkt.

0.003	2013-01-11

 [ Bug Fixes ]
 - Avoid triggering this issue in test suite.

 [ Documentation ]
 - Document issue in older Perls where packages crash if they import
   Sub::NonRole without applying the attibute to any subs.

0.002	2013-01-04

 - Added: Support for MooseX::Role::Parameterizable roles.

0.001	2013-01-03	Initial release
